<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>They have been busy filming TOWIE's 10th anniversary series. </p>

<p>And Amber Turner and Dan Edgar looked in the throes of love as they filmed scenes at a pig farm in Essex on Wednesday.</p>

<p>The reality star, 27, put on a busty display in a ribbed vest top which she teamed with high-waisted flared jeans and trainers.     </p>

